spec_data.Name: fawkes-plugin-openni-pcl-frombuf
spec_data.Description:
This package contains a Fawkes plugin reads a FireVision buffer and creates
a point cloud from it. This can be used for example to split acquisition
and processing in separate Fawkes instances.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Wed 20 Sep 2017 05:15:52 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Fawkes plugin to create point clouds from FireVision buffer
